text: Aliannis Ramírez (born 23 September 1997) is a Cuban water polo player. She was a member of the Cuba women's national water polo team at the 2019 Pan American Games and 2019 World Aquatics Championships. == References == == Other websites == * 5th straight pan am games Category:1997 births Category:Living people Category:Cuban water polo players
